//www.nbcnews.com/tech/security/meta-allows-repeat-scam-artists-target-seniors-report-says-rcna344068</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/tech/security/meta-allows-repeat-scam-artists-target-seniors-report-says-rcna344068</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260511-meta-medicare-scams-jg-c0c227.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1600" width="2400"><media:credit>Justine Goode</media:credit><media:text type="plain">In scam ads viewed by the researchers, viewers were promised free money via Medicare. </media:text><media:description type="plain">In scam ads viewed by the researchers, viewers were promised free money via Medicare. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260511-meta-medicare-scams-jg-c0c227.jpg" height="1600" width="2400"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 02:00:41 GMT</pubDate><title>Fake Trump and Oprah ads fuel a wave of Medicare scams on Facebook, report says</title><updateDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 02:00:41 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Tue, 12 May 2026 06:51:08 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Trump Mobile phone release date remains uncertain</description><expires>2056-05-12T06:50:17.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">f_vert_brk_trump_mobile_phone_260511</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/trump-mobile-phone-release-date-remains-uncertain-263148101745</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/f_vert_brk_trump_mobile_phone_260511/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Trump Mobile phone release date remains uncertain</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/video/shorts/trump-mobile-phone-release-date-remains-uncertain-263148101745"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_0